i2wzkb","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/i2wzkb/using_internet_like_its_1999"},{"short_id":"g3dptp","created_at":"2026-04-24T09:00:54.000-05:00","title":"Did we lose notifications for comment replies?","url":"","score":7,"flags":0,"comment_count":3,"description":"\u003cp\u003eIt would appear that we no longer get a notification in our Lobsters inbox for replies to comments or new comments on stories we submitted.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI remember a similar thing happened a few years ago, and was intentional (the DB side of things was too slow), but that was fixed. Was this intentional or did we hit a regression or is this purely a me problem?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e(Thank you to everyone who makes Lobsters possible. I know the support burden is nonzero and I hate to add to the pile.)\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"It would appear that we no longer get a notification in our Lobsters inbox for replies to comments or new comments on stories we submitted.\r\n\r\nI remember a similar thing happened a few years ago, and was intentional (the DB side of things was too slow), but that was fixed. Was this intentional or did we hit a regression or is this purely a me problem?\r\n\r\n(Thank you to everyone who makes Lobsters possible. I know the support burden is nonzero and I hate to add to the pile.)","submitter_user":"lorddimwit","user_is_author":true,"tags":["meta"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/g3dptp","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/g3dptp/did_we_lose_notifications_for_comment"},{"short_id":"kcggjp","created_at":"2026-04-24T08:54:15.000-05:00","title":"A quick look at Mythos run on Firefox: too much hype?","url":"https://xark.es/b/mythos-firefox-150","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"withzombies","user_is_author":false,"tags":["security","vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/kcggjp","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/kcggjp/quick_look_at_mythos_run_on_firefox_too"},{"s